<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> ritual act • ritualistic act</xh5><p> <i>ritual act—</i>an activity which happens as part of a tradition: Herein lies the explanation of how the act of bathing could have become a <u>ritual act</u> sanctioned by many religions.</p><p> <i>ritualistic act—</i>an activity which follows the same pattern every time it is used: I love tea because I love the <u>ritualistic act</u> of making and drinking tea.</p> </entry>
